Application design for students to record and transmit his/her levy(dues) payment to the association.

CanvasApp.Name: pal_nacospaymentapp_d0b8c
CanvasApp.Description: 1. The App makes payment of NACOS fee easier and less stressful. 2. Automation of manual process of receipt issuing. 3. Automation of workflow between the financial department and the president's office. 4. The students upload a transaction payment receipt on the app receipt processor. 5. Payment details is entered into the app by the student and submitted. 6. An automated printable payment receipt is generated and printed out to the student. 7. The approval of the payment is done by the FinSec in the canvas app and business process flow. 8. A notification email is sent to the president of payment details.
